p: The booster vaccine used was subunit aluminum hydroxide adsorbed influenza vaccine containing HA and NA proteins from the influenza virus A/turkey/Turkey/1/05 (H5N1). Sixty participants (40 vaccinees, 20 placebos from the previous phase II study) have been enrolled and received one dose of the H5 inactivated influenza vaccine (IIV) 1 year after the H5N2 vaccination. The total follow-up time was 90 days.
